headline: Fifth Third’s Laurent Desmangles, Linda W. Clement-Holmes Recognized as 2024 Most Influential Corporate Directors by Savoy Magazine
summary: CINCINNATI, November 21, 2024--Fifth Third directors Laurent Desmangles and Linda W. Clement-Holmes have been named to Savoy Magazine’s Most Influential Corporate Directors list.
